;Bulk solvent terms included in Fob file created with standard X-PLOR script.

Residues simultaneously refined in two or more conformations are:
Val53, Leu66, Ser86, Lys87, Leu99, Ser110, Ser113, Ser130, Lys159, 
Asp165, Ser166, Ser170, Gln175, Ser217, Lys230, Ser236, Ser244.

Disordered waters are: 
HOH350 which is close to HOH537;
HOH749 WHICH IS CLOSE TO HOH811.
His40 and HIS91 are MONOPROTONATED ON THE EPSILON NITROGEN.
HIS57 is MONOPROTONATED on the delta nitrogen.
